portals.mazeScript: Temple Of The Gate to Ekirth's Tomb

scripts.text: Finally, you stand before the second Great Gate. The Second Realm lies behind you, the way to the Third Realm is open. The Gate flickers and pulses before you; one more step on your journey to escape from the Maze.

scripts.mazeScript: Temple Of The Gate endgame cck

scripts.text: A low stone altar stands here. Dried blood cakes the surface.
A stone shaft descends from the floor of the room, it's end lost in darkness.
The pillar is covered with reliefs depicting evil looking frogs and snakes devouring eachother.
A low stone altar stands in the center of the chamber, squat and mostly unremarkable. Examining it, you note a small slot in the surface.
Without warning, the runes on the floor and ceiling pulse with deadly light!

mouseClickScript.text: You decide against jumping into the bottomless pit.

You strike the bell as hard as you are able, but no sound emerges.

Perhaps you need something heavier?
